Primary Goals

The system SHALL:

Provide centralized visibility into project activity
Aggregate GitHub repository data into actionable metrics
Detect project risk indicators
Provide AI-generated contextual recommendations
Improve project manager response speed
Support multiple projects per user
Support scalable future feature expansion
3.2 MVP Goals

The MVP release SHALL include:

GitHub OAuth authentication
Project dashboard
GitHub repository integration
Project metrics aggregation
Search and filtering
Basic AI-driven insights (statistical analysis)
Near real-time dashboard updates via polling
Notifications
Role-based access control
Activity feed
Usage analytics

The MVP SHALL NOT include:

Machine learning model training
Predictive forecasting models
Enterprise SSO
Native mobile applications
Multi-organization tenancy
Real-time WebSocket streaming
Custom workflow builders